## Final Phase: Create Pull Request

**IMPORTANT:** After all phases are completed and verified, create a Pull Request using the GitHub CLI.

### PR Creation Steps

1. **Ensure all changes are committed and pushed:**
```bash
cd {{ worktree_path }}
git push -u origin {{ branch_name }}
```

2. **Create the Pull Request with detailed description:**
```bash
gh pr create \
  --base {{ base_branch }} \
  --head {{ branch_name }} \
  --title "feat({{ feature_slug }}): [Brief description]" \
  --body "$(cat <<'PRBODY'
## Summary

[Provide a clear, concise summary of what this PR implements]

## Feature: {{ feature_slug }}

### Overview
[Describe the feature and its purpose]

### Changes Made

